#ad Saving lives, one organ at a time ❤️ @lifeshareok 

Join me in making a difference. Register as an organ donor today and give life a second chance. More than 600 Oklahomans and 100,000+ people across the country are waiting on a lifesaving transplant. 

When it comes to organ donation, doctors always prioritize your life first!! Together, we can make a life-saving impact. 

Go to Lifeshareok.org to learn more

LifeShare is local non-profit organization dedicated to recovering organs and tissue for transplant. They work with hospitals, transplant centers, and donors to make the donation process easier. 

Did you know that one donor can save up to 8 lives and enhance up to 75 through tissue donation. Organ donation only becomes an option when all life-saving efforts have been exhausted. It's a way to give someone else a second chance at life. 

You can register to donate at LifeShareOK.org or when getting a new driver's license ❤️
